  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1673130/extras/9d54da8b40bcb9b90d55ceb9aca3d056.poster.avif?t=1765839356\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1673130/extras/9d54da8b40bcb9b90d55ceb9aca3d056.webm?t=1765839356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1673130/extras/9d54da8b40bcb9b90d55ceb9aca3d056.mp4?t=1765839356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Blue Protagonist is being imprisoned and tortured in a small cell by three characters:   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Real Pain, the prison's boss who is red and has mustache. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Biggest Vain, a giant and mysterious knight who prevents prisoners from escaping. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Smallest Stain, a psychopath who enjoys killing others with a shotgun.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But suddenly, the door opens and now the only thing he wants is vengeance.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help him exit his cell and jump over the obstacles on his way to find and kill everyone who has made him suffer. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Storytelling using gameplay, with a few cutscenes and no dialogue.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Minimalist art and music.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 unconventional boss fights.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 levels, each set in a different location.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Influenced by the works of Albert Camus, specifically <i>The Stranger</i> and <i>The Myth of Sisyphus.</i></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1673130/extras/9d54da8b40bcb9b90d55ceb9aca3d056.poster.avif?t=1765839356\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1673130/extras/9d54da8b40bcb9b90d55ceb9aca3d056.webm?t=1765839356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1673130/extras/9d54da8b40bcb9b90d55ceb9aca3d056.mp4?t=1765839356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Blue Protagonist is being imprisoned and tortured in a small cell by three characters:   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Real Pain, the prison's boss who is red and has mustache. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Biggest Vain, a giant and mysterious knight who prevents prisoners from escaping. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Smallest Stain, a psychopath who enjoys killing others with a shotgun.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But suddenly, the door opens and now the only thing he wants is vengeance.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help him exit his cell and jump over the obstacles on his way to find and kill everyone who has made him suffer. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Storytelling using gameplay, with a few cutscenes and no dialogue.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Minimalist art and music.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 unconventional boss fights.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 levels, each set in a different location.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Influenced by the works of Albert Camus, specifically <i>The Stranger</i> and <i>The Myth of Sisyphus.</i></p></li></ul>",
